item.title: cedec
item.description: Cedec Swimwear company was founded in 1973 by Pierre Cedec. The main goal of the company is to produce high quality swimwear that is comfortable and suitable for every type of swimmer. For more than 30 years, they have been producing and selling their own brand of swimwear in Europe and the United States. In 1997, Cedec became a member of the International Swimwear Association (ISA). Today, Cedec Swimwear is represented in more than 100 countries worldwide.
